/www.linkedin.com/search/results/people/?keywords=Company%20Name%20recruiter\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"careers_url\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"recruiters\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": []\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nAfter the batch, run the status command again and print this exact marker on its own line:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n`=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE energy <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"exit_code\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":0,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"completed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}}\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/ai-batch-0001-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE ai <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/ai-batch-0004-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE ai <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/consulting-batch-0005-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE consulting <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"exit_code\\\\\\\":0,\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"completed\\\\\\\"}}\\\\n\\\",\\\"exit_code\\\":0,\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\"}}\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/retail.jsonl:118:{\\\"type\\\":\\\"item.completed\\\",\\\"item\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"item_40\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"agent_message\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"=== SECTOR retail STATUS ===\\\\nFile: job/sectors/recruiter-retail.json\\\\nPhase: coverage | Companies: 101 | Unpopulated: 0 | Missing descriptions: 87 | Below 10 contacts: 101\\\\nRecruiters: 210\\\\n\\\\n=== SECTOR_BAT