edin_company_url\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/snap-inc-co/\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"linkedin_url_verified\\\\\\\": true,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"recruiter_search_url\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/people/?keywords=Snap%20Inc.%20recruiter\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"careers_url\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"recruiters\\\\\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Laila Forghani\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Senior Recruiter, University Programs / Early Career Technical Recruiting\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"linkedin_url\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/lailafor\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"email\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"location\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Los Angeles, CA, United States\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"focus_area\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Early Career & Technical Recruiting (SWE intern and new grad)\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"connected\\\\\\\": false,\\\\n          \\\\\\\"messaged\\\\\\\": false,\\\\n          \\\\\\\"responded\\\\\\\": false,\\\\n          \\\\\\\"date_contacted\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"notes\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Senior Recruiter - University Programs / Early Career and Technical Recruiting at Snap Inc. (LA). Leads full-cycle recruitment for core engineering intern and early career SWE roles. Passionate about early career talent; multiple recommendations highlight her work in university and early-career hiring. Active with Snap summer intern programs and recognition for early career hiring excellence.\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\",\\\"exit_code\\\":0,\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\"}}\\njob/swarm/sectors/energy.md:128:`=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE energy <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===`\\njob/swarm/sectors/proptech.md:128:`=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE proptech <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-desc